('clown fish',FALSE,'https://acnhcdn.com/latest/MenuIcon/Fish40.png','https://acnhcdn.com/latest/BookFishIcon/FishKumanomiCropped.png','https://acnhcdn.com/latest/FtrIcon/FtrFishKumanomi.png',650,'Sea','X-Small','Medium','Medium',0,'5–6','NA','NA','NA','All day','All day','All day','All day','All day','All day','NA','NA','NA','All day','All day','All day','NA','NA','NA','NA','NA','NA','All day','All day','All day','1x1','No','Few can deny the delightful qualities of the clown fish. These vibrant fishes make their home among venomous anemones. It''s a mutually beneficial arrangement. The clown fish_finds safety in the anemone''s wriggling arms, as well as leftover scraps of food. In return, clown fish_ward off parasites and predators for the anemone. Thus these colorful fish_remind us of the importance of maintaining good cheer among our roommates.','I caught a clown fish! How many can fit in a carfish?',71,'Pet','Orange','Black','Fluorescent','L9qxZaMoBhwxvpMyh',49,'common',975),
('coelacanth',FALSE,'https://acnhcdn.com/latest/MenuIcon/Fish63.png','https://acnhcdn.com/latest/BookFishIcon/FishSirakansuCropped.png','https://acnhcdn.com/latest/FtrIcon/FtrFishSirakansu.png',15000,'Sea (rainy days)','XX-Large','Very Hard','Very Narrow',100,'1–2','All day','All day','All day','All day','All day','All day','All day','All day','All day','All day','All day','All day','All day','All day','All day','All day','All day','All day','All day','All day','All day','All day','All day','All day','2x1','Yes','The coelacanth is a deep-sea fish_that has been around since the age of the dinosaurs. They were long thought extinct, so when living specimens were discovered, it was quite a shock! Now I''ll just have to figure out where in the museum to display it— fish_or fossils!','Blast from the past! I caught a coelacanth! Think positive! Be a coela-CAN!',71,'Pet','Black','Black','Fluorescent','NjMZQ6Xi9NswEXnHH',80,'ultra rare',22500),
