(FALSE,'sabertooth skull','https://acnhcdn.com/latest/FtrIcon/FtrFossilSmilodonA.png',2500,'Sabertooth Tiger','Chief actor in my most terrifying nightmares, the Sabertooth Tiger was a mighty predator of long ago. Its most famous feature, obviously, is its razor-sharp, eight-inch-long, t-t-te-tee-te-tee...FANGS! I''m sorry—this is so unprofessional of me. Come on, Blathers! Stiff upper beak, eh wot! While no one has seen a living specimen for some 10,000 years, we must remain ever vigilant!',87,'Brown','Brown','2x2','Assessing fossils','Room 3',NULL,'Not for sale','4xkrLpphWXubgtRPw','No'),
